<doc id="626931" wikidata="Q3845676" url="?curid=626931" title="Molo people">
<text>Molo is an ethnic group in Blue Nile state in Sudan.

They number less than thousand and speak Molo, a Nilo-Saharan language. Most of them or all of them are Muslims.

